dct_title_s: Central-Kobenhavn, Turistkort = Copenhagen tourist map, the central area
dct_description_sm: Denmark. Geodaetisk Institut. Legend is in Danish and English. Map shows public transportation routes. Index to institutions, businesses, schools, etc. on margin. Verso: Street index, list of museums and points of interest.
